  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation results are reported from bench-top experiments comparing predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values against measured values across five flow-speed operating points. The structured provenance linking each validation result to its generating analysis activity is partially absent; one result record was entered without a wasGeneratedBy reference to the corresponding simulation run activity.",
