    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team determined that the available evidence is sufficient for the intended low-assurance submission context. Validation results across four of five operating points show NIH predictions within 20% of measured values. The missing provenance link on operating point 1 validation result was noted as an administrative gap; the underlying simulation data were described in the technical report narrative. The team accepted the package at low assurance level pending remediation of the provenance record and completion of not-assessed factors.",
